Head of Video Collaboration, 8x8
With Voximplant we were able to add calls to and from the phone network into our video conferencing solution within a few weeks. Their versatile REST API's have given us all the control we need - we've almost never needed to do something that we weren't able to. Their great international coverage lets us provide dial-in service all over the world.
